#: ../../S/scribble.rst:5
msgid "scribble"
msgstr "scribble"

#: ../../S/scribble.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../S/scribble.rst:9
msgid ""
"To modify a data structure in a random and unintentionally destructive way. "
"\"Bletch! Somebody's disk-compactor program went berserk and scribbled on "
"the i-node table.\" \"It was working fine until one of the allocation "
"routines scribbled on low core.\" Synonymous with :ref:`trash`\\; compare "
":ref:`mung`\\, which conveys a bit more intention, and :ref:`mangle`\\, "
"which is more violent and final."
msgstr ""
"データ構造をランダムかつ意図せず破壊的なやり方で変更すること。「ちぇっ! 誰かのディスクコンパクタプログラムが暴走してi-"
"nodeテーブルにscribbleした。」「あの割り当てルーチンのひとつが low core にscribbleするまでは問題なく動いていた。」\\ "
":ref:`trash`\\ と同義。もう少し意図を伝える\\ :ref:`mung`\\ や、より暴力的で決定的な\\ :ref:`mangle`\\"
" と比較せよ。"
